                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Configuration keys in CommonConfigurationKeys.java should be cleaned up and documented (javadoc comments, appropriate *-default.xml descriptions).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
